with the age of stellar population parameters would be linked with the
history of star formation and dynamical evolution. Aims. We aim to
investigate the structures of the outer Galaxy, such as the scale
length, disc truncation, warp and flare of the thin disc and study their
dependence with age by using 2MASS data and a population synthesis model
