in which case the closest encounter found is the K7 dwarf <ASTROBJ>GL
710</ASTROBJ>, which has a 90\% probability of coming within 0.10-0.44 pc
in about 1.3 Myr. A larger perturbation may have been caused by
<ASTROBJ>gamma Microscopii</ASTROBJ>, a G6 giant with a mass of about
