  Volume                   = {845},

  Abstract                 = {{We use the first Gaia data release, combined with the RAVE and APOGEE
spectroscopic surveys, to investigate the origin of halo stars within
{\lsim} 3 kpc from the Sun. We identify halo stars kinematically as
moving at a relative speed of at least 220 km s$^{-1}$ with
respect to the local standard of rest. These stars are generally less
