  Volume                   = {643},

  Abstract                 = {{We report on high-resolution echelle spectroscopy of 20 giant stars in
the Galactic old open cluster NGC 6791, obtained with Hydra at the WIYN
telescope. High-precision radial velocity allows us to isolate 15 bona
fide cluster members. From 10 of them we derive a global
