giants. Here, we discuss the reasons for the RC narrowness in several
sets of observational data, its fine structure, and the presence of
systematic changes in the RC properties as regards age, metallicity, and
the observed passband. These factors set the limits on the validity and
accuracy of several RC methods defined in the literature.
