  Volume                   = {110},

  Abstract                 = {{Rotation is thought to drive cyclic magnetic activity in the Sun and
Sun-like stars. Stellar dynamos, however, are poorly understood owing to
the scarcity of observations of rotation and magnetic fields in stars.
Here, inferences are drawn on the internal rotation of a distant
Sun-like star by studying its global modes of oscillation. We report
