  Abstract                 = {{We observed a small sample of 5 radio-quiet QSOs with integral field
spectroscopy to search for possible extended emission in the Ly\$$\backslash$alpha\$
line. We subtracted the QSO point sources using a simple PSF
self-calibration technique that takes advantage of the simultaneous
availability of spatial and spectral information. In 4 of the 5 objects
