LAMOST DR2 that have not been observed by APOGEE. This demonstrates that
precise individual abundances can be measured from low-resolution
spectra, and represents the largest catalog of [C/M], [N/M], masses and
ages to date. As as result, we greatly increase the number and sky
coverage of stars with mass and age estimates.
