roughly 100 km s$^{-1}$ kpc$^{-1}$ and flattens
considerably at greater l, reaching a maximum rotation of 75 km
s$^{-1}$. We compare our rotation curve and velocity
dispersion profile both to the self-consistent model of Zhao and to
