the Galactic thin disk. <BR /> Methods: We use high-resolution spectra
(FEROS, ESPADONS, NARVAL) to measure the abundances of several light
(Na, Al), {$\alpha$} (Mg, Si, S, Ca), and heavy elements (Y, Zr, La, Ce,
