  Abstract                 = {{Context. Gaia Data Release 1 (DR1) contains astrometric results for more
than 1 billion stars brighter than magnitude 20.7 based on observations
collected by the Gaia satellite during the first 14 months of its
operational phase. <BR /> Aims: We give a brief overview of the
