  Volume                   = {580},

  Abstract                 = {{Context. The inner disc, which links the thin disc with the bulge, has
been somewhat neglected in the past because of the intrinsic
difficulties in its study, among which crowding and high extinction.
Open clusters located in the inner disc are among thebest tracers of its
chemistry at different ages and distances. <BR /> Aims: We analyse the
