  Pages                    = {521-543},
  Volume                   = {358},

  Abstract                 = {{We present a generalization of the multiphase chemical evolution model
(CEM) applied to a wide set of theoretical galaxies with different
masses and evolutionary rates. This generalized set of models has been
computed using the so-called universal rotation curve from Persic,
Salucci {\amp} Steel to calculate the radial mass distribution of 44
