  Year                     = {2016},

  Month                    = jun,
  Pages                    = {114},
  Volume                   = {823},

  Abstract                 = {{The mass of a star is arguably its most fundamental parameter. For red
giant stars, tracers luminous enough to be observed across the Galaxy,
