  Abstract                 = {{We combine H I 21 cm observations of the Milky Way, M31, and the local
galaxy population with QSO absorption-line measurements to geometrically
model the three-dimensional distribution of infalling neutral-gas clouds
(''high-velocity clouds'' (HVCs)) in the extended halos of low-redshift
