$\lt$ W$\gt$ compared to the stars with $\{$T$\}$$_{{eff}$$\}$ $\backslash$lt 6000 K.
And their azimuthal velocity increases when | z| increases. This
peculiar motion in the warmer stars is likely because they are young and
