dex <BR /> Conclusions: The {$\alpha$} enhancement ({\ap}+0.4 dex) found in
the observed giant stars of Terzan 1 is consistent with previous
measurements on other, more metal-rich bulge clusters, which suggests a
rapid chemical enrichment.

Based on data taken at the ESO/VLT Telescope, within the observing
program 093.D-0179(A).
